OL,5,G1900 The Shadows Final Tour
OL,6,     FHank Marvin, Bruce Welch and Brian
OL,7,     FBennett are reunited for The
OL,8,     FShadows' final tour in 2004,
OL,9,     Ftreating crowds to a medley of
OL,10,     Ftheir greatest hits, including
OL,11,     FApache, Living Doll and FBI.
OL,12,G2200 The Doors: Classic Albums
OL,13,     FFormer band members of The Doors
OL,14,     Fdiscuss their self-titled debut
OL,15,     Falbum, which featured The End and
OL,16,     FLight My Fire, and the lyrical
OL,17,     Fgenius of Jim Morrison.
OL,18,G2300 Opry Live
OL,19,     FPrepare to be blown away by
OL,20,     Fperformances from Opry member
OL,21,     FCarrie Underwood, Bailey Zimmerman
OL,22,     Fand Old Dominion.
